        "content": "<p>2 messages were moved here from <a href=\"#narrow/channel/287929-mathlib4/topic/.60fun_prop.60.20sometimes.20unfolds.20semireducible.20definitions\">#mathlib4 &gt; &#96;fun_prop&#96; sometimes unfolds semireducible definitions</a> by <span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"890057\">ZhiKai Pong</span>.</p>",
