    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/34345\">#34345</a> is the culprit and this has been discussed in the PR but a fix hasn't been found. cc <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"310045\">@Eric Wieser</span></p>",
        "id": 575029767,
        "sender_full_name": "ZhiKai Pong",
        "timestamp": 1771622460
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>from the PR:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It's happy to use @Differentiable.continuous ... ?someNormedSpace but appears to get upset with @Differentiable.continuous ... ?someNormedSpace ... (?someContSMul : ContinuousSMul .. ?someNormedSpace), because the latter tries to postpone a synthesis whose type is itself a postponed synthesis.</p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 575030893,
        "sender_full_name": "ZhiKai Pong",
        "timestamp": 1771622985
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Thanks for the ping; there is an easy fix of duplicating the theorem statement for normed spaces, as I discuss <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/34345#discussion_r2726522942\">in the PR</a></p>",
        "id": 575047015,
        "sender_full_name": "Eric Wieser",
        "timestamp": 1771633212
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>The correct fix would be to change <code>fun_prop</code>, namely to <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0b16e4ae9dc4c332dad36f20d031f79ea10391ec/Mathlib/Tactic/FunProp/Core.lean#L48-L103\"><code>synthesizeArgs</code></a></p>",
        "id": 575047020,
        "sender_full_name": "Eric Wieser",
        "timestamp": 1771633218
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>This needs to handle multiple iterations of postponed arguments, not just a single iteration</p>",
        "id": 575047221,
        "sender_full_name": "Eric Wieser",
        "timestamp": 1771633391
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Yeah there should be a while loop that keeps on going over the arguments and should break once you fail to make a progress.</p>",
        "id": 575092554,
        "sender_full_name": "Tomas Skrivan",
        "timestamp": 1771685646
    }
